<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmation de retrait - Bictrary</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2d3748;
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            height: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .divider {
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .info-label {
            color: #4a5568;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        .amount-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f6f9fc 0%, #eef2f6 100%);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2b6cb0;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .currency {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #4a5568;
        }
        .tx-hash {
            word-break: break-all;
            font-family: monospace;
            background-color: #edf2f7;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 14px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .button {
            display: block;
            width: 200px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4299e1 0%, #3182ce 100%);
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(66, 153, 225, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(66, 153, 225, 0.3);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            background-color: #48bb78;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .wallet-address {
            font-family: monospace;
            background-color: #edf2f7;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 14px;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/harissonola/my-cdn/main/img/bactrary-logo.png" alt="Bictrary" class="logo">
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="status-badge">Retrait Réussi</div>
            <h1 class="title">Confirmation de Retrait</h1>
            
            <p>Bonjour,</p>
            <p>Votre demande de retrait a été traitée avec succès. Voici le récapitulatif de votre transaction :</p>

            <div class="amount-container">
                <div style="color: #718096; font-size: 14px;">Montant reçu</div>
                <div class="amount">{{ net_amount }} <span class="currency">{{ currency|upper }}</span></div>
                <div style="color: #718096; font-size: 14px;">(Montant brut: {{ amount }} {{ currency|upper }})</div>
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Frais de retrait :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{ fees }} {{ currency|upper }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Adresse de destination :</span>
                <span class="wallet-address">{{ wallet_address }}</span>
            </div>
            {% if tx_hash %}
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Identifiant de transaction :</span>
                <span class="tx-hash">{{ tx_hash }}</span>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Date et heure :</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{ "now"|date("d/m/Y à H:i") }}</span>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 25px;">Les fonds devraient apparaître dans votre portefeuille sous peu. Si vous ne constatez pas le crédit dans les 24 heures, vous pouvez consulter votre profil.</p>

            <a href="{{ absolute_url(path('app_profile')) }}" class="button">Accéder à mon compte</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Cet email vous a été envoyé automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre.</p>
            <p>© {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Bictrary. Tous droits réservés.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>